{"tid":2097033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"地盤工疑阻打人 被控襲擊 聲稱受襲福建翁：警察唔會拉錯人","createTime":"2020-07-06T13:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T18:30:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ed1b4fd25bcd18710469df1ed37e1b57021d8b","tid":2097033,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075214&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEqGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=bbbac8e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075214&h=43e1196c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075214</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）市民去年9月15日到港島區「去港島行街」，其後發生警民衝突。有地盤工人被指當日在北角以鋁棍襲擊一名七旬漢的右臂，事後被控普通襲擊罪。被告否認控罪，案件今日（7月6日）於東區裁判法院開審，控方傳召聲稱受襲的72歲福建籍事主顏加星及其子顏原成，裁判官崔美霞裁定表面證供成立，案件明日（7月7日）續審，並由被告自辯。事主顏加星在庭上未能認出被告，只不斷稱：「警察唔會捉錯人！」，又指被告沒有用棍打過他，被盤問時更激動大罵：「你咁講即係話我同警察有關連！」"},{"pid":"2aa7a3fc301566811e792a6fc090a32b796f019f","tid":2097033,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"繼樂天之後，三叔都緊隨步伐賣港，公然使用殘體字<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2097014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2097014</a>"},{"pid":"fc64616b7cf41e2e280625020c6db143e8706a5c","tid":2097033,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa7a3fc301566811e792a6fc090a32b796f019f","tid":2097033,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"繼樂天之後，三叔都緊隨步伐賣港，公然使用殘體字<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2097014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2097014</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class